MEXICO CITY Lewis Hamilton will be crowned world champion for a sixth time in Mexico on Sunday if... + He finishes first (with fastest lap) and Valtteri Bottas finishes fourth + He finishes first with Bottas fifth + He finishes second with Bottas eighth (no fastest lap) + He finishes second with Bottas ninth + He finishes third (with fastest lap) with Bottas ninth + He finishes third with Bottas 10th (no fastest lap)  